{"tid":153212,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 南乳花生炆豬手","createTime":"2017-03-12T11:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T23:47:43.000Z","uid":74981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5d9dd83de5b4162e1cbc9d9a21f79b4b2e704d","tid":153212,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/aa5a66cd97c87810b9ff3053862dc4a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Faa5a66cd97c87810b9ff3053862dc4a1.jpg&h=59c142ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TA9jH4XWdy4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTA9jH4XWdy4&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c5440d9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TA9jH4XWdy4</a><br />\n<br />\n步驟慨述:<br />\n1. 豬手兩隻洗淨出水，出完洗乾淨，秘乾水備用<br />\n<br />\n2. 開獲燒熱，落油，中火爆香薑片，收細火爆南乳，贊酒<br />\n<br />\n3. 落豬手一齊爆透佢，然後落水2碗半，冰糖，少少蠔油，少少生抽，花生一碗，大火煮滾，襟蓋收細火炆30分鐘，完成。<br />\n<br />\n4. 如想再淋少少，再炆多10分鐘左右就好，唔好炆太耐，否則皮唔夠爽身，太淋就冇咁好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d898d11c1a36f02cc0ad3c31537f52112d7d8159","tid":153212,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"壯士斷臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed265e4baa0c91082deef65198686e7bd0d2e4b","tid":153212,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壯士斷臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f7129a6648452ace1c53b6d6a9c7c4cd594322","tid":153212,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:02:26.000Z","msg